WEBVTT

01:50.160 --> 01:51.320
Shang Ningyu.

01:51.880 --> 01:53.680
It's already the second semester of sophomore year.

01:53.680 --> 01:55.360
Why aren't you doing your homework?

01:55.360 --> 01:56.440
I'm telling you,

01:56.640 --> 01:59.170
Ruirui is studying extremely hard right now.

01:59.240 --> 02:00.680
If you don't make progress,

02:00.680 --> 02:02.200
be careful she might look down on you in the future.

02:02.200 --> 02:03.440
That's impossible.

02:03.560 --> 02:05.690
Ruirui isn't such a superficial girl.

02:05.840 --> 02:08.080
She will definitely see my inner depth.

02:08.440 --> 02:10.320
Doesn't Ruirui like drinking soda?

02:10.320 --> 02:11.360
Happy back to school.

02:11.360 --> 02:13.020
I brought some for you two too.

02:15.160 --> 02:16.240
Awesome.

02:16.440 --> 02:18.570
Since when did you become so generous?

02:20.120 --> 02:20.880
Ruirui.

02:22.040 --> 02:23.240
You have privileges.

02:23.240 --> 02:25.240
I bought you two bottles of

02:25.280 --> 02:26.810
soda in different flavors.

02:28.320 --> 02:28.980
Here you go.

02:30.040 --> 02:31.440
Is there soda for me?

02:35.200 --> 02:37.240
Qiao Yan, you're finally back.

02:37.280 --> 02:38.200
Did you miss me?

02:38.400 --> 02:39.840
Of course I did.

02:39.880 --> 02:40.480
Without you,

02:40.480 --> 02:42.320
our group feels incomplete.

02:44.760 --> 02:46.560
So the unpredictability of life

02:46.840 --> 02:48.600
is not just a phrase.

02:49.000 --> 02:50.130
These past few days,

02:50.280 --> 02:52.410
my mood has been like a roller coaster.

02:52.720 --> 02:55.320
Ups and downs.

02:56.440 --> 02:57.570
I suddenly realized

02:57.800 --> 02:59.200
that the people around us

02:59.320 --> 03:00.850
can really leave suddenly,

03:01.160 --> 03:02.620
and also return suddenly.

03:03.040 --> 03:06.440
We are completely helpless in the face of this impermanence.

03:06.640 --> 03:08.640
All we can do is cherish the present

03:09.240 --> 03:11.080
and cherish everyone around us.

03:11.520 --> 03:13.400
But what happened next

03:13.520 --> 03:16.200
made me realize just how fragile life is.

03:16.480 --> 03:19.160
Sometimes people leave without even saying goodbye,

03:19.160 --> 03:20.890
and they truly never come back.

03:23.600 --> 03:26.530
The subscriber you dialed is out of the service area.

03:29.120 --> 03:29.920
How is it?

03:30.120 --> 03:31.520
Did Xiaoyu answer the phone?

03:31.520 --> 03:34.380
They were sent to the disaster area for relief work.

03:35.480 --> 03:36.560
Is it dangerous?

03:37.000 --> 03:38.040
I trust him.

03:38.720 --> 03:40.980
I believe he can take good care of himself

03:41.480 --> 03:42.840
and the victims as well.

03:43.840 --> 03:46.720
Let's just stay at home and wait for news.

03:51.400 --> 03:54.440
So many people died in this earthquake.

03:54.880 --> 03:55.960
It's so tragic.

03:57.480 --> 03:59.160
Look at these young children.

03:59.840 --> 04:01.240
What are they going to do?

04:02.160 --> 04:04.280
I want to go to Wenchuan and join the rescue team.

04:04.280 --> 04:05.640
This is nonsense.

04:07.000 --> 04:09.320
Why would a student like you join a rescue team?

04:09.320 --> 04:10.560
The government will send people.

04:10.560 --> 04:12.920
Just focus on your studies and stop overthinking.

04:12.920 --> 04:15.650
On the way back, I thought about it the whole time.

04:15.920 --> 04:18.579
The country educates us and sends us to college.

04:18.880 --> 04:20.209
Isn't it so that one day,

04:20.360 --> 04:21.240
we can contribute to our country

04:21.240 --> 04:22.000
and society,

04:22.200 --> 04:23.840
doing our part?

04:24.480 --> 04:26.340
They need people there right now.

04:26.480 --> 04:27.600
I think I should go.

04:27.880 --> 04:29.560
What can you do if you go?

04:30.520 --> 04:31.760
Can you do rescue work,

04:31.760 --> 04:33.290
or help people move things?

04:33.320 --> 04:34.720
Aren't you just messing around?

04:34.720 --> 04:36.080
I can be a volunteer.

04:36.680 --> 04:38.320
I can help distribute supplies.

04:38.320 --> 04:39.840
I can also help take care of the wounded.

04:39.840 --> 04:40.840
I can move bricks.

04:40.840 --> 04:41.840
I can do anything.

04:41.920 --> 04:43.560
What is wrong with you?

04:43.760 --> 04:45.440
When did you suddenly become so stubborn?

04:45.440 --> 04:46.760
Ever since he went to Zhicheng,

04:46.760 --> 04:48.000
he's become like this.

04:48.000 --> 04:49.920
Look how he's mingled with those kids.

04:49.920 --> 04:51.640
Please don't be prejudiced against them.

04:51.640 --> 04:52.570
What prejudice?

04:53.640 --> 04:56.300
Look at the grades of the students in your class.

04:56.960 --> 04:59.080
Alright, then tell me,

04:59.240 --> 05:01.720
what exactly is so good about these kids?

05:03.640 --> 05:06.800
Some of them, to inherit their father's legacy,

05:07.760 --> 05:10.400
choose to join the army and defend the country.

05:11.000 --> 05:12.040
Is that not good?

05:12.520 --> 05:13.400
Some of them,

05:13.800 --> 05:15.860
to save a classmate with depression,

05:16.240 --> 05:17.600
didn't hesitate to fall off a cliff together,

05:17.600 --> 05:19.000
saving a life and a family.

05:19.000 --> 05:19.960
Is that not good?

05:20.920 --> 05:22.760
They helped two lonely elderly people

05:22.760 --> 05:25.290
regain their passion and confidence in life.

05:25.600 --> 05:26.880
Are they really

05:27.760 --> 05:28.560
not good?

05:31.000 --> 05:33.280
You used to say that having money and power is good,

05:33.280 --> 05:34.640
and being first is good.

05:35.280 --> 05:37.080
But ever since I went to Zhicheng

05:37.240 --> 05:38.800
and met them, I realized

05:39.520 --> 05:41.850
there are many kinds of good in this world.

05:43.240 --> 05:44.240
Some kinds of good

05:45.120 --> 05:45.960
are greater

05:46.880 --> 05:48.080
and more meaningful.

05:49.560 --> 05:50.360
And what I need

05:51.800 --> 05:53.400
is exactly that kind of good.

05:54.800 --> 05:55.860
Do you understand?

06:16.280 --> 06:18.400
Stop hiding it. I saw everything.

06:20.200 --> 06:22.520
You little brat. You've grown up.

06:30.320 --> 06:32.040
As for going to Wenchuan,

06:32.440 --> 06:33.880
don't even think about it.

06:33.880 --> 06:35.840
The situation there is very dangerous right now.

06:35.840 --> 06:36.880
Your mother and I

06:37.000 --> 06:38.560
only have one precious son.

06:38.960 --> 06:41.020
We will never let you take such a risk.

06:41.520 --> 06:42.120
All right.

06:54.120 --> 06:54.880
Your school

06:54.920 --> 06:57.040
will definitely organize a donation tomorrow.

06:57.040 --> 06:58.280
Take this money

06:58.600 --> 07:01.000
and donate it along with your pocket money.

07:01.000 --> 07:02.520
Consider it a contribution to the country

07:02.520 --> 07:04.080
and the people of Wenchuan.

07:07.120 --> 07:08.960
Brat, stop overthinking.

07:09.680 --> 07:11.480
Study hard and rest early.

07:12.680 --> 07:15.610
Remember to give the check to your teacher tomorrow.

07:17.000 --> 07:17.600
I know.

07:21.240 --> 07:22.000
Thank you.

07:37.400 --> 07:40.720
On May 12th, the eighth day of the fourth lunar month,

07:41.000 --> 07:44.460
a massive 7.8 magnitude earthquake struck the Wenchuan area.

07:45.080 --> 07:46.360
In the face of this great disaster,

07:46.360 --> 07:49.420
when one place is in trouble, help comes from all sides.

07:49.640 --> 07:51.520
We gather here today

07:52.480 --> 07:54.680
not only to mourn our lost compatriots,

07:55.560 --> 07:57.400
but also to pray for the living.

07:58.120 --> 08:00.400
May there be no more pain for those in heaven.

08:00.400 --> 08:02.600
May the living pull themselves together

08:02.600 --> 08:04.460
and embrace a brand new tomorrow.

08:05.600 --> 08:07.880
Please light the candles in your hands

08:08.280 --> 08:12.880
and let us observe a three-minute silence for the deceased.

08:24.760 --> 08:26.040
This disaster

08:26.560 --> 08:28.760
has taken away too many precious lives.

08:29.640 --> 08:31.880
Although I haven't seen it with my own eyes,

08:31.880 --> 08:33.480
I can feel the pain.

08:34.480 --> 08:35.720
It is said that only after experiencing sorrow

08:35.720 --> 08:37.200
do we know how to cherish.

08:38.360 --> 08:39.320
Yes.

08:40.320 --> 08:41.760
At this moment,

08:42.520 --> 08:44.960
they can still stand properly by my side.

08:46.280 --> 08:50.000
We all still have healthy and safe families.

08:51.080 --> 08:53.400
What a lucky thing it is.

08:57.640 --> 08:58.640
Before,

08:59.120 --> 09:01.600
I thought 'compatriot' was just a word.

09:02.680 --> 09:03.600
At this moment,

09:04.360 --> 09:07.720
this word seems to have seeped into our souls,

09:08.080 --> 09:09.480
taken on flesh and blood,

09:10.040 --> 09:12.160
and become vivid lives

09:12.960 --> 09:14.640
that tug at our heartstrings.

09:49.880 --> 09:53.280
2008 was truly an extraordinary year,

09:54.080 --> 09:56.140
filled with reluctance and emotion.

09:56.640 --> 09:57.600
Mutou and I

09:57.720 --> 09:59.920
seem to have grown up a lot in an instant.

10:00.360 --> 10:02.360
But more surprises and wonders

10:02.600 --> 10:05.400
have actually just begun.

10:18.840 --> 10:22.000
This... this is too unreal.

10:26.360 --> 10:27.620
This is Mr. Zhen Shuai.

10:27.920 --> 10:29.050
Yuanbao, say hello.

10:30.840 --> 10:31.400
Hello.

10:31.480 --> 10:32.520
Hello, Mr. Zhen.

10:33.000 --> 10:33.560
Hello.

10:36.800 --> 10:38.600
Summer vacation is coming soon.

10:38.800 --> 10:40.760
From now on, every weekend, Mr. Zhen

10:40.760 --> 10:43.240
will come to tutor you two in physics and math.

10:43.240 --> 10:44.440
Three hours a day.

10:44.600 --> 10:46.000
You two need to work hard.

10:46.200 --> 10:47.280
Got it, Auntie.

10:49.680 --> 10:52.800
Mr. Zhen is a student at Qingbei University.

10:53.120 --> 10:55.240
He got excellent grades back then

10:55.280 --> 10:57.160
and got admitted to a university in Beijing.

10:57.160 --> 11:00.400
He is very experienced with the 12th grade and the college entrance exam.

11:00.400 --> 11:01.330
And he is about to

11:01.400 --> 11:03.360
prepare for the graduate school entrance exam.

11:03.360 --> 11:05.640
He is just using his spare time

11:05.840 --> 11:07.080
to work part-time.

11:07.760 --> 11:08.360
Right?

11:08.840 --> 11:09.570
Yes, Auntie.

11:09.840 --> 11:11.960
I work part-time every winter and summer vacation

11:11.960 --> 11:13.120
to give high school students

11:13.120 --> 11:14.380
one-on-one tutoring.

11:14.520 --> 11:16.480
Sharing some of my study methods

11:16.520 --> 11:18.450
and exam experience with everyone

11:18.560 --> 11:19.960
is very meaningful to me.

11:20.080 --> 11:21.360
Oh my god.

11:21.840 --> 11:23.570
Zhen Shuai is really handsome.

11:24.120 --> 11:26.040
Will Yuanbao be smitten?

11:26.440 --> 11:26.960
Um,

11:27.160 --> 11:29.160
Mr. Zhen, let's go to that room for class.

11:29.160 --> 11:29.800
Okay, Auntie.

11:29.800 --> 11:31.240
You two get ready quickly. Class is starting.

11:31.240 --> 11:32.360
This way, this way.

11:35.680 --> 11:37.080
Study hard with me.

11:37.160 --> 11:38.320
Don't be boy-crazy.

11:39.080 --> 11:40.210
I'll test you later.

11:40.520 --> 11:42.000
Got it. You're so nagging.

11:42.080 --> 11:43.120
Hurry up, you two.

11:43.120 --> 11:44.400
Okay, coming.

11:46.080 --> 11:47.200
Actually, let's look

11:47.200 --> 11:49.520
at the trend charts for Person A and Person B.

11:49.520 --> 11:51.160
Using the method we showed,

11:51.240 --> 11:53.480
A and B are both ruled out, right?

11:53.560 --> 11:54.960
Then let's look at C.

11:55.120 --> 11:56.280
Then option C.

12:00.120 --> 12:01.320
Bro, you know what?

12:01.680 --> 12:03.240
There was a top student in our school.

12:03.240 --> 12:04.520
He came back to do a part-time job

12:04.520 --> 12:06.680
during the holiday to tutor the seniors.

12:06.680 --> 12:08.920
My cousin happened to be his student.

12:09.200 --> 12:11.560
Not only did he help my cousin get into his school,

12:11.560 --> 12:13.360
but they also ended up together.

12:14.200 --> 12:18.160
That's what you call a double harvest in love and studies.

12:18.920 --> 12:19.920
How interesting.

12:23.400 --> 12:24.440
What's wrong?

12:26.240 --> 12:28.880
I need to use the restroom.

12:33.800 --> 12:34.730
Let's continue.

12:35.360 --> 12:36.160
For this one,

12:37.400 --> 12:38.920
Option B, none are equal.

12:39.880 --> 12:41.160
We can rule this one out too.

12:41.160 --> 12:42.560
Why are you back already?

12:43.720 --> 12:44.580
I lost the urge.

12:47.080 --> 12:49.410
Do you find the questions a bit difficult?

12:50.160 --> 12:53.560
Actually, learning math consists of three main parts.

12:53.760 --> 12:55.840
First is learning the concepts.

12:56.320 --> 12:57.240
We need to clearly understand

12:57.240 --> 12:59.100
all the concepts in the textbook,

12:59.280 --> 13:01.280
and apply them flexibly.

13:01.880 --> 13:04.810
Then the second point is the sea of questions tactic.

13:06.360 --> 13:08.080
If he tutors Ruirui,

13:08.360 --> 13:10.760
she will definitely faint from happiness.

13:11.040 --> 13:13.280
Mr. Zhen Shuai is so handsome.

13:32.400 --> 13:34.530
What's wrong? Are you feeling unwell?

13:36.040 --> 13:38.000
Not at all. I'm feeling great.

13:43.640 --> 13:45.100
Fifty students in a class,

13:45.120 --> 13:47.320
in a 100-meter test,

13:47.600 --> 13:49.730
their results are shown in the figure.

13:49.760 --> 13:50.800
So let's see,

13:50.840 --> 13:53.300
the results of the first two students are...

13:58.600 --> 13:59.280
Sir.

14:00.560 --> 14:04.400
Um, you should head back

14:04.520 --> 14:05.920
and get some rest.

14:06.240 --> 14:07.040
It's fine.

14:08.000 --> 14:09.280
Don't worry about the time.

14:09.280 --> 14:11.340
I'm more than willing to help you out.

14:14.680 --> 14:16.410
Sir, your words are so helpful.

14:16.520 --> 14:18.280
Can I ask you a few more questions?

14:18.280 --> 14:19.160
Sure, go ahead.

14:21.360 --> 14:22.080
Yuanbao.

14:23.000 --> 14:25.000
Don't you want to go to the restroom?

14:26.920 --> 14:28.040
I don't want to.

14:28.120 --> 14:29.520
I haven't had much water.

14:35.480 --> 14:37.010
Look at the question first.

14:47.920 --> 14:49.650
Sir, I'm going to the restroom.

14:50.560 --> 14:51.960
Sir, could you give me

14:52.000 --> 14:52.800
your chat ID

14:52.840 --> 14:54.080
or phone number?

14:54.320 --> 14:55.160
In case I have any questions later.

14:55.160 --> 14:56.120
Right.

14:56.160 --> 14:57.680
You should leave a chat ID, sir.

14:57.680 --> 14:58.480
Just add mine.

14:58.560 --> 15:00.800
We will both ask you if we don't understand something.

15:00.800 --> 15:01.400
Okay.

15:05.360 --> 15:06.160
Here.

15:06.280 --> 15:07.080
Okay.

15:11.600 --> 15:14.480
This question is the last one in the college entrance exam.

15:14.480 --> 15:17.740
So my predictions are actually quite accurate every year.

15:25.280 --> 15:27.010
We use our rule of probability.

15:28.680 --> 15:29.280
Sir.

15:29.720 --> 15:31.400
You've been talking for so long.

15:31.400 --> 15:33.000
Are you bursting to go?

15:33.200 --> 15:33.680
Do you not know

15:33.680 --> 15:34.840
where our bathroom is?

15:34.840 --> 15:35.120
No.

15:35.120 --> 15:35.920
I'll take you.

15:35.920 --> 15:36.360
Mu Qingyun.

15:36.360 --> 15:37.560
The bathroom is right over there.

15:37.560 --> 15:38.240
Come with me.

15:38.240 --> 15:38.800
Student.

15:38.840 --> 15:39.200
I.

15:39.400 --> 15:40.520
You go first. I'm not in a hurry.

15:40.520 --> 15:41.960
You go first.

15:44.520 --> 15:45.120
Come in,

15:45.200 --> 15:45.880
Mu Qingyun.

15:45.960 --> 15:46.520
No.

15:52.160 --> 15:53.240
I... I'll go back first.

15:53.240 --> 15:54.300
Teacher! Teacher!

15:54.480 --> 15:57.000
Well, I feel safe with you here.

15:57.520 --> 15:59.800
Could you explain that question to me again?

15:59.800 --> 16:00.160
What is it?

16:00.160 --> 16:01.480
What was I explaining? Um...

16:01.480 --> 16:02.120
What?

16:02.440 --> 16:03.700
What was it again? I...

16:05.880 --> 16:08.040
Come, the food is good today.

16:08.320 --> 16:08.920
Come.

16:09.040 --> 16:10.760
How is the tutoring with Mr. Zhen Shuai?

16:10.760 --> 16:12.040
Can you understand him?

16:12.040 --> 16:12.720
Yes.

16:12.800 --> 16:14.160
Mr. Zhen Shuai teaches very well.

16:14.160 --> 16:15.240
I study very hard.

16:15.920 --> 16:16.650
That's good.

16:18.720 --> 16:21.200
I thought we wasted our money.

16:21.440 --> 16:22.920
How could it be a waste?

16:23.920 --> 16:25.880
When Zhen Shuai was in high school,

16:26.040 --> 16:27.960
he devoted himself entirely to his studies,

16:27.960 --> 16:29.840
which is why he is so successful now.

16:29.840 --> 16:31.000
He is now in college

16:31.040 --> 16:32.960
with a full scholarship.

16:33.240 --> 16:35.440
You two should learn from him, okay?

16:36.200 --> 16:37.040
Don't worry, Auntie.

16:37.040 --> 16:38.240
I definitely won't let down

16:38.240 --> 16:40.160
you and Mr. Zhen Shuai's expectations.

16:40.160 --> 16:41.440
Auntie, you know what?

16:41.800 --> 16:42.640
Mr. Zhen Shuai...

16:42.640 --> 16:44.360
Talk less while eating.

16:44.640 --> 16:45.040
Okay, thanks.

16:45.040 --> 16:45.800
It's bad for your stomach.

16:45.800 --> 16:46.720
Auntie, you know what?

16:46.720 --> 16:48.920
Mr. Zhen Shuai knows so much.

16:49.160 --> 16:51.020
He knows everything under the sun

16:51.120 --> 16:52.850
and is a walking encyclopedia.

16:54.800 --> 16:56.000
I choked on chili oil.

16:57.360 --> 16:59.160
He knows everything under the sun,

16:59.160 --> 17:01.600
is a walking encyclopedia, and is very learned.

17:01.600 --> 17:03.160
He really is outstanding.

17:03.560 --> 17:05.720
He also told me a lot about college...

17:10.319 --> 17:10.920
Well,

17:11.640 --> 17:12.700
I sprained my neck.

17:13.720 --> 17:16.160
This child is always so easily startled.

17:16.319 --> 17:17.240
What are you doing?

17:17.240 --> 17:19.040
Why do you keep interrupting me?

17:22.000 --> 17:22.720
Go on.

17:23.760 --> 17:25.960
Mr. Zhen Shuai also told me a lot

17:25.960 --> 17:27.520
about college life.

17:27.680 --> 17:29.040
I will definitely work hard,

17:29.040 --> 17:30.000
get into college,

17:30.000 --> 17:31.930
and absolutely won't let you down.

17:32.120 --> 17:33.920
College life is so interesting.

17:35.360 --> 17:36.360
There's a mosquito.

17:36.360 --> 17:37.620
Where is the mosquito?

17:37.960 --> 17:39.680
Sit down and eat your food.

17:44.160 --> 17:45.160
Really, Yuanbao?

17:45.480 --> 17:46.810
Then you must work hard.

17:47.000 --> 17:48.320
As long as you get into college,

17:48.320 --> 17:50.600
Auntie will buy you whatever you want.

17:51.040 --> 17:51.600
Really?

17:51.800 --> 17:54.400
Don't worry, I will burn the midnight oil,

17:54.480 --> 17:55.240
study hard,

17:55.320 --> 17:56.560
not make Grandpa and Grandma angry,

17:56.560 --> 17:57.690
and not let you down.

17:57.880 --> 17:58.840
Good.

17:58.960 --> 18:01.280
Come, Yuanbao, eat more.

18:01.520 --> 18:03.880
Good health gives you the motivation to study.

18:03.880 --> 18:04.560
Exactly.

18:05.040 --> 18:07.700
I just like kids who get into good universities.

18:08.040 --> 18:08.760
Yuanbao,

18:09.200 --> 18:11.460
you need to study hard with Mr. Zhen Shuai

18:11.640 --> 18:13.370
and get into a good university.

18:13.480 --> 18:14.000
Right.

18:14.040 --> 18:14.640
Keep it up.

18:14.640 --> 18:16.170
Grandpa is waiting for you.

18:17.000 --> 18:17.920
Don't worry.

18:17.960 --> 18:20.960
I feel that after Mr. Zhen Shuai's guidance this time,

18:21.160 --> 18:23.890
my brain seems to have had a flash of inspiration.

18:24.200 --> 18:25.130
As for my grades,

18:25.280 --> 18:26.080
I promise

18:26.200 --> 18:28.840
I will definitely make even further progress.

18:29.040 --> 18:29.680
A UFO!

18:30.200 --> 18:32.200
A UFO! Mom, look!

18:36.600 --> 18:37.760
It looks like a light bulb.

18:37.760 --> 18:39.490
Mom, doesn't it look like a UFO?

18:40.720 --> 18:41.800
Doesn't it?

18:42.800 --> 18:43.960
You're so jumpy.

18:44.080 --> 18:46.480
Can you try to keep up with my studying pace?

18:46.680 --> 18:48.080
I advise you to take it easy.

18:48.080 --> 18:49.240
Don't brag too much.

18:49.440 --> 18:50.480
Yuanbao is right.

18:50.760 --> 18:52.240
You need to learn from him.

18:52.440 --> 18:53.320
Zhen Shuai, Zhen Shuai.

18:53.320 --> 18:55.520
All you talk about all day is Zhen Shuai.

18:56.040 --> 18:56.760
Mom,

18:57.440 --> 18:59.120
do you think your son is handsome?

18:59.120 --> 19:00.450
My son is also handsome.

19:01.600 --> 19:03.130
I'm the truly handsome one.

19:09.880 --> 19:11.540
Why did you ask me to come here?

19:12.840 --> 19:14.500
Summer vacation is coming up.

19:14.880 --> 19:16.200
I want you to do me a favor.

19:16.200 --> 19:18.800
You want me to go to your house to tutor Yuanbao?

19:19.640 --> 19:20.640
The great Alpha

19:21.360 --> 19:23.040
is actually asking for my help.

19:23.040 --> 19:24.400
What are you up to?

19:25.720 --> 19:27.960
A stronger opponent has appeared.

19:28.680 --> 19:31.400
What kind of enemy makes you so nervous?

19:32.120 --> 19:33.580
Are they stronger than me?

19:36.640 --> 19:37.700
I'll tell you what.

19:37.880 --> 19:39.280
Go and see for yourself.

19:47.640 --> 19:48.800
He's too strong.

19:49.600 --> 19:50.960
Let's team up and take him down.

19:50.960 --> 19:52.400
Why else would I call you?

19:53.040 --> 19:53.960
Mr. Zhen,

19:54.280 --> 19:57.600
this is Yuanbao and Qingyun's classmate, Meng Jingu.

19:57.960 --> 19:59.680
He's also an excellent student.

19:59.680 --> 20:01.410
But I heard you are even better,

20:01.480 --> 20:03.560
and he has some questions for you.

20:03.920 --> 20:06.680
Would you mind teaching him as well?

20:06.720 --> 20:08.120
No problem. Don't worry.

20:08.320 --> 20:09.280
That's great.

20:09.560 --> 20:10.600
You guys go study.

20:10.720 --> 20:12.760
I'll get you some water and fruit.

20:13.000 --> 20:14.040
Thank you, Auntie.

20:14.040 --> 20:14.970
You're welcome.

20:15.320 --> 20:16.380
Thank you, Auntie.

20:16.480 --> 20:18.320
Great, another top student.

20:18.800 --> 20:19.480
Let's go.

20:19.480 --> 20:20.360
Go study now. Let's go.

20:20.360 --> 20:21.600
Go on.

20:21.680 --> 20:22.340
Go quickly.

20:24.880 --> 20:27.440
Uniform circular motion is variable motion.

20:27.960 --> 20:29.960
Especially questions 24 and 25.

20:30.040 --> 20:31.840
You must all mark these two questions.

20:31.840 --> 20:33.570
It will probably be on the test.

20:34.360 --> 20:35.080
Come.

20:35.320 --> 20:37.000
Don't just talk about the questions.

20:37.000 --> 20:37.930
Have some water.

20:38.080 --> 20:39.080
Thank you, ma'am.

20:39.440 --> 20:40.370
You're welcome.

20:40.440 --> 20:42.400
Mr. Zhen, thanks for your hard work.

20:42.400 --> 20:44.260
It's nothing, ma'am. It's my job.

20:45.400 --> 20:47.060
Come with me to get some fruit.

20:47.400 --> 20:49.400
Yuanbao, help my mom get some fruit.

20:49.680 --> 20:50.920
Why are you so lazy,

20:51.440 --> 20:52.720
asking me to get fruit?

20:58.480 --> 20:59.240
Mr. Zhen,

20:59.680 --> 21:01.320
I have a few physics questions here.

21:01.320 --> 21:02.780
Can you explain them to us?

21:09.000 --> 21:10.360
These questions are very difficult.

21:10.360 --> 21:12.040
They shouldn't be on the college entrance exam.

21:12.040 --> 21:12.680
Sir,

21:13.080 --> 21:14.340
our head teacher said,

21:14.480 --> 21:16.480
if this year's physics exam is easy,

21:16.680 --> 21:18.000
next year's will be particularly hard.

21:18.000 --> 21:20.130
Was your year's exam especially easy?

21:22.240 --> 21:23.970
Let me take a good look, hold on.

21:32.520 --> 21:33.720
Eat the fruit.

21:34.160 --> 21:35.280
Eat more fruit.

21:35.520 --> 21:37.450
I'll get you more when you're done.

21:38.360 --> 21:39.160
Study hard.

22:30.680 --> 22:32.640
I'll go get some more fruit.

22:37.600 --> 22:38.880
Sir, almost done?

22:41.640 --> 22:42.480
Take a look.

22:42.640 --> 22:43.440
This question

22:43.880 --> 22:45.410
should be solved like this.

23:14.960 --> 23:15.800
Mr. Zhen,

23:16.280 --> 23:18.340
you seem to have calculated it wrong.

23:24.480 --> 23:25.320
Your

23:25.760 --> 23:26.880
seems wrong.

23:27.400 --> 23:28.120
Sir,

23:28.440 --> 23:30.440
could we both be wrong together?

23:30.800 --> 23:33.160
Our Jingu is first in the whole grade.

23:33.520 --> 23:34.980
If you think you're right,

23:35.360 --> 23:36.880
why are you still asking me?

23:36.880 --> 23:37.760
We just wanted to see

23:37.760 --> 23:39.760
if you are a real teacher or a fake one.

23:39.760 --> 23:41.280
What if you lead students astray?

23:41.280 --> 23:42.210
What do you mean?

23:43.120 --> 23:45.250
Did you come here to test me on purpose?

23:45.720 --> 23:46.720
We wouldn't dare.

23:47.280 --> 23:48.560
You are a top student,

23:49.040 --> 23:51.240
we are humbly asking for your guidance.

23:53.040 --> 23:53.920
Mu Qingjun,

23:54.480 --> 23:56.240
even if you can solve a difficult question correctly,

23:56.240 --> 23:59.040
it doesn't mean you will pass the college entrance exam smoothly.

23:59.040 --> 24:00.570
Your foundation is so poor,

24:00.920 --> 24:02.640
and your learning attitude is improper.

24:02.640 --> 24:04.700
You won't get into college like this.

24:05.360 --> 24:07.120
Who are you saying won't get into college?

24:07.120 --> 24:08.920
What's with your attitude? I'm talking about you.

24:08.920 --> 24:10.520
How can you curse someone not to get into college?

24:10.520 --> 24:11.560
I won't get into college?

24:11.560 --> 24:12.800
How could I not get into college?

24:12.800 --> 24:13.930
Who are you cursing?

24:14.880 --> 24:15.680
Mu Qingjun,

24:16.360 --> 24:17.420
what are you doing?

24:17.480 --> 24:18.560
Are you rebelling?

24:22.760 --> 24:24.760
The teacher said I can't get into college. He cursed me.

24:24.760 --> 24:25.360
Sit down.

24:26.720 --> 24:28.280
Sorry, Auntie.

24:28.520 --> 24:31.600
I just think his attitude towards studying is extremely incorrect.

24:31.600 --> 24:33.600
This will be very bad for his future.

24:35.240 --> 24:36.200
You two make up.

24:45.480 --> 24:46.520
Let's start.

24:47.760 --> 24:49.000
I'm sorry.

24:50.040 --> 24:51.640
Love you.

24:53.320 --> 24:57.600
Because we are a family,

24:58.040 --> 25:01.920
a family that loves each other.

25:02.120 --> 25:04.480
It takes fate to bring us together,

25:04.760 --> 25:07.040
and heart to cherish each other.

25:07.160 --> 25:11.840
Why let the clouds cover your eyes?

25:12.360 --> 25:15.080
Ms. Zhen, I am really sorry

25:15.800 --> 25:17.640
for putting you in a difficult position.

25:17.640 --> 25:18.600
The children are still young.

25:18.600 --> 25:20.560
Please don't take it to heart.

25:21.040 --> 25:22.600
I will clean it up later

25:23.800 --> 25:25.130
and teach them a lesson.

25:25.720 --> 25:26.800
It's fine, Auntie.

25:27.120 --> 25:29.000
It was my fault today.

25:29.080 --> 25:30.140
I acted on impulse.

25:30.920 --> 25:32.480
I'll be going now.

25:32.640 --> 25:33.440
Okay.

25:33.640 --> 25:34.440
Ms. Zhen,

25:35.040 --> 25:36.680
I will call you later.

25:38.920 --> 25:39.600
All right.

25:40.120 --> 25:41.000
Goodbye, Auntie.

25:41.000 --> 25:42.200
Goodbye, Ms. Zhen.

25:42.960 --> 25:44.280
Take care on your way.

25:45.080 --> 25:45.680
Goodbye.

25:54.760 --> 25:56.120
What's wrong with you today?

25:56.120 --> 25:58.050
Why did you almost get into a fight?

25:58.640 --> 25:59.480
No, Mom.

26:00.000 --> 26:02.480
Well, I was a bit impulsive.

26:03.280 --> 26:03.960
But

26:04.440 --> 26:07.700
Mr. Zhen really doesn't know how to solve a lot of problems.

26:08.000 --> 26:08.720
I guess

26:08.960 --> 26:10.820
maybe because he went to college,

26:11.240 --> 26:13.440
he forgot all the high school problems.

26:13.600 --> 26:15.530
He's not even as good as Meng Jingu.

26:16.400 --> 26:19.160
He has been through it and is a top student.

26:19.280 --> 26:21.010
Can you be a little more humble?

26:23.040 --> 26:24.560
Auntie, how about this?

26:24.920 --> 26:26.680
Let me tutor Yuanbao

26:26.680 --> 26:28.610
and Qingjun this summer vacation.

26:30.480 --> 26:31.880
I'm more familiar with them

26:31.880 --> 26:33.240
and easier to get along with.

26:33.240 --> 26:33.880
Besides,

26:34.120 --> 26:35.960
we are learning the same grade's curriculum.

26:35.960 --> 26:36.840
Every year's college entrance examination

26:36.840 --> 26:38.280
has a different focus.

26:38.520 --> 26:39.800
It's better to rely on ourselves than others,

26:39.800 --> 26:42.200
and it can also save you some money, Auntie.

26:43.600 --> 26:45.200
Jingu is such a good kid.

26:46.360 --> 26:47.960
So, do you two agree?

26:48.120 --> 26:48.800
I agree.

26:48.960 --> 26:49.880
I agree.

26:50.680 --> 26:52.340
All right, it's settled then.

26:52.640 --> 26:54.560
Thank you for your hard work, Jingu.

26:54.560 --> 26:55.200
Great.

26:55.320 --> 26:57.120
The house will be much livelier.

27:00.720 --> 27:01.480
Wait, Mom.

27:03.640 --> 27:06.240
I don't think Meng Jingu needs to come for the whole summer vacation.

27:06.240 --> 27:08.000
Right? Two days is enough.

27:08.560 --> 27:09.320
Not enough.

27:10.040 --> 27:11.500
Knowledge is systematic.

27:11.840 --> 27:14.770
I can come for the whole summer vacation, no problem.

27:15.520 --> 27:17.180
All right, it's settled then.

27:26.400 --> 27:27.520
I am really

27:28.200 --> 27:31.660
the mantis stalking the cicada, unaware of the oriole behind.

27:32.680 --> 27:33.480
Jingu.

27:35.280 --> 27:36.800
Look, what is this?

27:41.120 --> 27:43.760
Tickets to the opening ceremony of the Beijing Olympics.

27:43.760 --> 27:45.160
Haven't you always wanted to get into

27:45.160 --> 27:47.240
the Physics Department of Qingbei University?

27:47.240 --> 27:48.720
It just so happens that our family of three

27:48.720 --> 27:51.520
can take this opportunity to look around Beijing.

27:51.680 --> 27:53.920
You can go to the Qingbei University you've been dreaming of,

27:53.920 --> 27:54.760
to take a look.

27:55.000 --> 27:56.880
You're about to start your senior year.

27:56.880 --> 27:58.480
Let's go out and relax a bit.

27:59.120 --> 28:00.760
And when we come back,

28:00.840 --> 28:02.880
you can devote yourself entirely to the college entrance exam.

28:02.880 --> 28:03.720
But...

28:04.400 --> 28:05.240
What's wrong?

28:05.920 --> 28:07.760
I've already agreed with my classmates

28:07.760 --> 28:10.320
to take extra classes together during the summer vacation.

28:10.320 --> 28:13.050
Do you still need extra classes with your grades?

28:13.640 --> 28:14.760
I'm acting as the tutor.

28:14.760 --> 28:15.600
Tutor?

28:15.880 --> 28:16.840
Is it paid?

28:17.160 --> 28:18.000
It's unpaid.

28:20.080 --> 28:21.000
Jingu.

28:21.160 --> 28:24.360
Look, your dad and I have already booked the tickets.

28:24.760 --> 28:26.920
Other students take tutoring classes anywhere.

28:26.920 --> 28:28.960
Besides, you're not a teacher.

28:29.080 --> 28:30.520
What kind of tutoring are you doing?

28:30.520 --> 28:32.680
This is our family of three's

28:32.760 --> 28:33.960
first trip together.

28:34.200 --> 28:37.320
How about you cancel the tutoring?

28:37.440 --> 28:38.440
All right.

28:39.120 --> 28:41.600
In the past, I always asked him to look up,

28:42.000 --> 28:44.160
to only care about winning, losing, and profit,

28:44.160 --> 28:45.620
instead of true feelings.

28:45.800 --> 28:47.960
But now I realize I was wrong.

28:48.680 --> 28:49.280
Dad.

28:50.200 --> 28:51.860
You brat, you're still young.

28:52.520 --> 28:54.180
In the best years of your life,

28:54.840 --> 28:56.080
do what you want to do.

28:56.840 --> 28:58.480
Don't let the expectations of me and your mom

28:58.480 --> 28:59.280
hold you back.

28:59.440 --> 29:01.200
Never live for us.

29:01.520 --> 29:02.920
Be brave and be yourself.

29:05.440 --> 29:06.770
Why are you suddenly...

29:06.880 --> 29:08.000
I am your father.

29:08.360 --> 29:10.000
And you are my son.

29:10.440 --> 29:11.840
I used to think,

29:11.920 --> 29:14.080
what does a little kid like him know?

29:14.640 --> 29:16.440
But I've come to realize more and more

29:16.440 --> 29:18.920
that sometimes he is also my teacher.

29:20.360 --> 29:21.440
You brat, you know what?

29:21.440 --> 29:22.520
Actually,

29:22.960 --> 29:24.520
it's also my first time being a dad.

29:24.520 --> 29:25.200
Maybe

29:25.280 --> 29:27.540
this dad is sometimes too authoritarian

29:27.840 --> 29:29.900
and rarely considers your feelings.

29:30.000 --> 29:32.520
From now on, let's learn from each other.

29:32.840 --> 29:33.700
How about that?

29:34.080 --> 29:34.840
Thank you.

29:40.960 --> 29:43.090
Are you really not going to tell Jingu?

29:46.320 --> 29:48.650
It's not certain that it's malignant yet.

29:48.840 --> 29:51.120
Telling him will only distract him.

29:52.160 --> 29:52.960
Forget it.

29:55.680 --> 29:57.040
I'll go to Beijing with you.

29:57.040 --> 29:58.970
We'll get it checked out properly.

30:32.360 --> 30:35.090
Yuanbao hasn't quite gotten the hang of science.

30:36.720 --> 30:37.580
Let me tell you.

30:38.440 --> 30:39.920
She actually works very hard,

30:39.920 --> 30:41.080
but she tends to overthink things.

30:41.080 --> 30:42.210
She's too stubborn.

30:45.760 --> 30:48.600
She also has tons of embarrassing moments.

30:48.720 --> 30:49.480
Let me tell you,

30:49.480 --> 30:50.200
over the years,

30:50.200 --> 30:52.520
I've come to know all her strengths and weaknesses.

30:52.520 --> 30:53.000
Don't you think

30:53.000 --> 30:54.320
I describe her perfectly?

30:54.320 --> 30:55.250
I'm telling you.

30:55.480 --> 30:57.280
The other time she was in...

30:57.960 --> 30:59.720
Who are you saying is overthinking?

30:59.720 --> 31:00.920
Who is overthinking?

31:01.560 --> 31:02.760
When did you get back?

31:03.400 --> 31:04.400
Don't just stare at me.

31:04.400 --> 31:05.560
Who exactly likes to overthink?

31:05.560 --> 31:06.520
I do.

31:06.760 --> 31:08.220
I like to overthink, okay?

31:17.360 --> 31:19.560
Jingu, thanks for your hard work today.

31:19.640 --> 31:21.080
Be careful on your way home.

31:21.080 --> 31:23.000
Send me a message when you get home.

31:23.000 --> 31:24.200
Don't worry, Auntie.

31:24.400 --> 31:25.520
Then see you tomorrow.

31:25.520 --> 31:26.040
Okay.

31:26.320 --> 31:27.800
Then Auntie, Mutou,

31:28.080 --> 31:29.200
I'll be going back too.

31:29.200 --> 31:31.400
Okay, go to sleep as soon as you get back.

31:31.840 --> 31:32.520
Take it easy.

31:32.520 --> 31:33.080
Mom.

31:33.360 --> 31:35.000
Um, I'll walk them out.

31:35.160 --> 31:36.890
Okay, make it quick. It's late.

31:38.280 --> 31:39.080
Okay.

31:42.040 --> 31:43.770
Desk mate, thank you for today.

31:44.360 --> 31:45.120
Don't mention it.

31:45.120 --> 31:45.320
Okay.

31:45.320 --> 31:46.400
Go back and rest early.

31:46.400 --> 31:46.640
Okay.

31:46.640 --> 31:47.600
I'll go back too.

31:48.400 --> 31:49.400
See you tomorrow.

31:49.560 --> 31:50.560
See you tomorrow.

31:51.400 --> 31:52.640
Hurry up and go sleep.

31:56.480 --> 31:58.440
Okay.

32:00.080 --> 32:01.080
See you tomorrow.

32:01.160 --> 32:01.840
See you.

32:01.880 --> 32:02.760
Definitely.

32:15.640 --> 32:17.600
Coming.

32:20.440 --> 32:21.280
Jingu.

32:21.360 --> 32:22.000
Auntie.

32:23.120 --> 32:24.180
You're back again.

32:25.160 --> 32:27.200
Auntie, my house key is missing.

32:27.480 --> 32:28.640
I don't know if I forgot to bring it

32:28.640 --> 32:30.240
or left it in Qingjun's room.

32:30.920 --> 32:32.000
Come on in.

32:32.080 --> 32:33.160
Let's look for it together.

32:33.160 --> 32:34.000
Okay.
